entries.complete: You have survived the Suprise Attack!
entries.split_quest_alert: Pilot, we have a serious problem. The Rebels have attacked another ship. It would appear that they were uncertain what ship had the list. You are needed to help protect that other craft.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Destroy the Rebel X-wings
entries.title_d: A group of Rebels have come in a bit too late in order to stop you from making the delivery. Destroy them.
